<h1>FAQ</h1>

<h2>What is Global Shapers Community?</h2>

<p>
Global Shapers Community is an initiative of the World Economic Forum that connects young leaders around the world.
</p>

<h2>What is Fukushima Hub?</h2>

<p>
Fukushima Hub is the local chapter of Global Shapers Community located in Fukushima, Japan.
</p>

<h2>How can I join?</h2>

<p>
Recruitment is conducted annually. Updates are announced through the official Instagram and WEF platform.
</p>

